{"tid":2214292,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"［支持本地音樂］有冇搞錯，月尾咁多本地音樂節目居然冇人講？","createTime":"2020-09-23T07:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T20:11:11.000Z","uid":97367,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a39ff0b998caf3cbc3df578d061889768302ec72","tid":2214292,"uid":97367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:01:29.000Z","msg":"冇人講咪我講囉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月過咗大半啦，但係呢個月最後一個禮拜對樂迷來講將會相當精彩 <br />\n事關來緊將會有唔少節目睇，支持本地音樂既你一定唔可以錯過啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">#1 wow and flutter Live@Home</span></strong></ins><br />\n久違既wow and flutter Live@Home返來啦<br />\n唔淨止今個月尾，由今日起連續四個星期三既lineup都出咗啦<br />\n有興趣既即管睇下啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：9.23 (Wed) <span class=\"red\"><strong>係呀，今晚呀</strong></span> <br />\n時間：11pm<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wowandflutterhk/photos/a.573347482825797/1628969187263616/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwowandflutterhk%2Fphotos%2Fa.573347482825797%2F1628969187263616%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=e92e965b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wowandflutterhk/photos/a.573347482825797/1628969187263616/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-nrt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/119843571_1628969190596949_1034242364926326928_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Bd60q0ys9aAAX_a_YOG&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-nrt1-1.xx&amp;oh=f01dfeefe988eb0975c241024a16e383&amp;oe=5F91485A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-nrt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F119843571_1628969190596949_1034242364926326928_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DBd60q0ys9aAAX_a_YOG%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-nrt1-1.xx%26oh%3Df01dfeefe988eb0975c241024a16e383%26oe%3D5F91485A&h=54639873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n｜wow and flutter｜Live@Home｜Coming Lineup｜<br />\n<br />\nCy Leo 何卓彥，香港口琴家，今年成立咗本地音樂廠牌 Ginger Muse 末薑，嚟緊亦都準備去紐約讀 jazz music嘅碩士課程。<br />\n<br />\n上個月佢推出咗全新專輯《Angel &amp; Demon 顛黑倒白》，將呢一年對香港嘅感受紀錄低，天使與魔鬼？好人定壞人？佢希望借新碟喺呢個紛擾嘅時代用音樂同大家講，我地依然能堅持選擇做正確嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n呢張專輯記載住 Cy Leo呢一年嘅心情同想法，當中多種嘅音樂類型就如唔同嘅情緒咁，時而平和，時而激昂，一路聽住就好似睇緊佢本日記咁！<br />\n<br />\n今次佢連同幾位朋友嚟到 Live@Home會首次直播演奏新碟嘅歌啊，星期三晚 wow and flutter嘅 YouTube channel見~<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\nwow and flutter FB：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wowandflutterhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwowandflutterhk%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=67cdb67d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wowandflutterhk/</a><br />\nwow and flutter youtube：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCmkPTPpGDGPwJgXO1g-e1Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCCmkPTPpGDGPwJgXO1g-e1Q&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=e0948da4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCCmkPTPpGDGPwJgXO1g-e1Q</a><br />\n來自今晚既演出單位，Cy Leo - Paris<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HLX6hTXaDAk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHLX6hTXaDAk&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=7e84173a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HLX6hTXaDAk</a>"},{"pid":"d64a4517436f9cbf52b2fb41b43dbd9e052f755c","tid":2214292,"uid":97367,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">#2 搶耳展演 Ear Up Showcase 2020</span></strong></ins><br />\n搶耳畀到唔少獨立音樂單位一個唔錯既演出平台<br />\n大家有興趣既可以留意下，畢竟佢地真係好需要你既支持 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：9.25 (Fri) - 9.27 (Sun)<br />\n時間：7pm<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/646670792952922/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%