>\nGordon Ho何景熙<br />\nPolypumpkins<br />\nTAOTAO<br />\nWHIZZ<br />\n<br />\n<strong>/ / LINE UP - 9.27 Sun 7pm / /</strong><br />\n<ins>表演嘉賓：</ins><br />\n陳嘉<br />\n<ins>搶耳單位：</ins><br />\nElly C<br />\nFranklin Telescope<br />\n留香瓊<br />\nMETER ROOM<br />\nSADJAY<br />\nwongguyshawn &amp; sumj.chan<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n大會亦都整咗個Spotify熱身歌單，畀大家認識下唔同單位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/6h1pPnw0YPFQBvLQfxTczi?si=ijnp2WoQSLOPKlN0USfWqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fopen.spotify.com%2Fplaylist%2F6h1pPnw0YPFQBvLQfxTczi%3Fsi%3Dijnp2WoQSLOPKlN0USfWqQ&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=f2812c86\" target=\"_blank\">https://open.spotify.com/playlist/6h1pPnw0YPFQBvLQfxTczi?si=ijnp2WoQSLOPKlN0USfWqQ</a>"},{"pid":"ce0c34274cfab1b153a281dbfdfced7d45b1d528","tid":2214292,"uid":97367,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T07:08:50.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">#3 Sunset Concert 2020</span></strong></ins><br />\n原定係演藝學院舉行既Sunset Concert今年會改由網上直播形式舉行<br />\n當中既演出單位間唔中都係音樂台提及過，特別係Tone Online Music Festival 過後有更多人認識Life Was All Silence<br />\n唔知今次佢地又會有咩搞作啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日期：9.30 (Wed)<br />\n時間：6pm<br />\n詳情：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/646670792952922/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fevents%2F646670792952922%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9rJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=3fd504f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/events/646670792952922/</a><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-nrt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/118883397_3439157276308912_8009700436190184711_n.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=SOzDyTwgZmAAX-2WitS&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-nrt1-1.xx&amp;oh=bf83973c4b225105a7e5d4ebb61c6b48&amp;oe=5F90F808\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscont